当前php版本对应的xdebug扩展到php安装目录的ext目录下</li><li>配置php.ini修改[Xdebug]模块</li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":146} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/RLOBTTTBNBQEUUXLX2O.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-146\"/><figcaption>xdebug配置</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>[Xdebug]<br> zend_extension = \"./php-nts-5.6.9\\ext\\php_xdebug.dll\"<br> xdebug.auto_trace = 0<br> xdebug.trace_output_dir = \"..\\php-nts-5.6.9\\Xdebug\"<br> xdebug.profiler_enable = 1<br> xdebug.profiler_output_dir = \"..\\php-nts-5.6.9\\Xdebug\\profiler\"<br> xdebug.max_nesting_level = 100<br> xdebug.remote_enable = 1<br> xdebug.remote_host = 127.0.0.1<br> xdebug.remote_port = 9427<br> xdebug.remote_handler = dbgp <br>xdebug.idekey = PHPSTORM </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2:配置PHPPHPStorm，如图：</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":147} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/KL85@FGXRSIYLOHC3-1024x600.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-147\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":148} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/ZUENPK38NZRMYN2__C-1024x600.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-148\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":149} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/6DOMV13RFQ@_JHCI92-1024x600.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-149\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>3：现在可以尽情的测试了。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":150} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/9Y0TLVV8KMBM5IFGF80-1024x649.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-150\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":151} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-cont