:11','2019-06-01 03:02:11','','未标题-1','','inherit','open','closed','','%e6%9c%aa%e6%a0%87%e9%a2%98-1-4','','','2019-06-01 11:02:11','2019-06-01 03:02:11','',0,'https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/未标题-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(184,1,'2019-06-01 14:58:48','2019-06-01 06:58:48','','1','','inherit','open','closed','','1-2','','','2019-06-01 14:58:48','2019-06-01 06:58:48','',154,'https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(185,1,'2019-06-01 14:59:14','2019-06-01 06:59:14','<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>1.   git服务器仓库创建</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>git  init  --bare  test.git</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>2.  编写git hook坚听仓库提交更新</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>vim  test.git/hooks/post-receive</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>#!/bin/bash<br>unset GIT_DIR<br>cd /www<br>git fetch --all<br>git reset --hard origin/master<br>exit 0</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>3.  服务器端克隆仓库到 /www</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>cd /www</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>git clone /home/gitrepo/test.git test   # 这里是前面我们创建的git仓库地址</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":184} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-184\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>4.  至此大功告成,在本地clone仓库并提交代码,然后去服务器/home/www/test/下查看是否自动更新代码</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->','git仓库自动拉取代码','','inherit','closed','closed','','154-revision-v1','','','2019-06-01 14:59:14','2019-06-01 06:59:14','',154,'https://long521.cn/2019/06/01/154-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(188,1,'2019-06-01 16:10:11','2019-06-01 08:10:11','<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>如果php已经安装了xdebug扩展九跳过安装步骤 </strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:verse -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-verse\">1.  官网下载与php版本对应的xdebug扩展源码<br>wget <a href=\"https://xdebug.org/files/xdebug-2.7.2.tgz\">https://xdebug.org/files/xdebug-2.7.2.tgz</a><br><br>2.  解压缩<br>tar -zxf xdebug-2.7.2.tar<br><br>3.  进入解压缩后的xdebug-2.7.2目录下<br>cd    xdebug-2.7.2.tar <br><br>4. 使用phpize生成对应的configure文件<br>/usr/local/php7.2/bin/phpize<br><br>5.  配置xdebug预安装<br>./configure --with-php-config=/usr/local/php7.2/bin/php-config<br><br>6. 开始编译安装<br>make -j  &amp;&amp; make install      # -j选项有提高编译速度<br><br>编译安装成功如图：<br><br></pre>\n<!-- /wp:verse -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":189} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/U@8OTH_EUY0TFUR8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-189\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>编辑php.ini开启xdebug扩展并配置一些选项</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:verse -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-verse\">1.&nbsp; &nbsp;找到你的php加载的php.ini<br>脚本运行phpinfo();查看加载的php.ini位置<br><br>2.&nbsp; &nbsp;vim&nbsp; /your-php-ini<br>----------------------------------------------------------------------<br>[Xdebug]<br>zend_extension = xdebug.so<strong><br></strong>xdebug.auto_trace = 0<br>xdebug.remote_autostart=On<br>xdebug.trace_output_dir = /tmp/xdebug<strong><br></strong>xdebug.profiler_enable = 1<br>xdebug.profiler_output_dir = /tmp/xdebug/profiler<strong><br></strong>xdebug.max_nesting_level = 100<br>xdebug.remote_enable = 1<br>xdebug.remote_host = 192.168.1.116&nbsp; &nbsp;# 这里写你的本机内网ip<br>xdebug.remote_port = 9427&nbsp; &nbsp; #&nbsp; 端口号后面要用<br>xdebug.remote_handler = dbgp<br>xdebug.idekey = PHPSTORM <br>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>3. 停止php-fpm 再启动<br>&nbsp;kill -INT `cat&nbsp; /usr/local/php7.2/var/run/php-fpm.pid`<br>或者<br>&nbsp;pkill php-fpm <br>或者<br>service php-fpm restart<br> <br></pre>\n<!-- /wp:verse -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>配置PHPStorm支持xdebug</strong></li><li></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":191} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/KL85@FGXRSIYLOHC3-1024x600-1024x600.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-191\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":192} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/NX@HB6REJ_E3T3ZTOH-1024x716.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-192\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>好了接下来可以测试了</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":194} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/YE6JSNXJF9P4PZP1CWF8W4-1024x494.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-194\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->','Linux配置PhpStorm Xdebug','','publish','open','open','','linux%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aephpstorm-xdebug','','','2019-08-22 19:10:24','2019-08-22 11:10:24','',0,'https://long521.cn/?p=188',0,'post','',0),(189,1,'2019-06-01 15:42:18','2019-06-01 07:42:18','','U@8`}~OTH$_E(UY[0TFUR$8','','inherit','open','closed','','u8oth_euy0tfur8','','','2019-06-01 15:42:18','2019-06-01 07:42:18','',188,'https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/U@8OTH_EUY0TFUR8.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(190,1,'2019-06-01 15:58:31','2019-06-01 07:58:31','','U@8`}~OTH$_E(UY[0TFUR$8','','inherit','open','closed','','u8oth_euy0tfur8-2','','','2019-06-01 15:58:31','2019-06-01 07:58:31','',188,'https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/U@8OTH_EUY0TFUR8-1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(191,1,'2019-06-01 15:58:44','2019-06-01 07:58:44','','KL85@FGXRSIYLOHC3-1024x600','','inherit','open','closed','','kl85fgxrsiylohc3-1024x600','','','2019-06-01 15:58:44','2019-06-01 07:58:44','',188,'https://long521.cn/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/KL85@FGXRSIYLOHC3-1024x600.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(192,1,'2019-06-01 16:06:20','2019-06-01 08:06:20','','N`X@H`B6RE}J_E3(T3ZT$OH','','inherit','open','closed','','nxhb6rej_e3t3ztoh','','','2019-06-01 1